    {
      "sort": 700000,
      "name": "Grappled",
      "type": "rule",
      "_id": "MsrEhBwmMcCXQkiT",
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 3
      },
      "image": {},
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<ul><li><p>A grappled creature’s speed becomes 0, and it can’t benefit from any bonus to its speed.</p></li><li><p>The condition ends if the grappler is incapacitated (see the condition).</p></li><li><p>The condition also ends if an effect removes the grappled creature from the reach of the grappler or grappling effect, such as when a creature is hurled away by the <em>thunderwave</em> spell.</p></li></ul>",
        "markdown": ""
      },
